<#import "template.ftl" as layout>
<@layout.emailLayout>

<div class="header">
  <a href="https://quantinar.com"><img width="100px" src="${url.resourcesUrl}/img/quantinar.png" alt="Quantinar Logo"></a>
  <a href="https://quantlet.com"><img width="100px" src="${url.resourcesUrl}/img/quantlet.png" alt="Quantlet Logo"></a>
  <a href="https://theida.net"> <img width="100px" src="${url.resourcesUrl}/img/ida.png" alt="IDA Logo"></a>
  <a href="https://blockchain-research-center.com"><img width="80px" src="${url.resourcesUrl}/img/brc.png" alt="BRC Logo"></a>
</div>

<h1>Welcome to the Q2 Ecosystem!</h1>

<p><strong>Hi ${firstName}!,</strong></p>

<p>Thank you for joining the <strong>Q2 Ecosystem</strong> – we're thrilled to have you on board!</p>

<p>You're now part of a growing global network of quantitative minds and innovators. But did you know Quantinar is just one part of a powerful ecosystem designed to accelerate your journey in machine learning research, coding, and data?</p>

<p>Let us introduce you to the full ecosystem:</p>

<div class="ecosystem-item">
  <p><strong>Quantinar</strong> – Our knowledge platform where you'll find expert-led courselets, insightful lectures, and curated learning paths for researchers at all levels.</p>
</div>

<div class="ecosystem-item">
  <p><strong>Quantlet</strong> – A platform packed with high-quality, reproducible code notebooks for statistics, quant finance, machine learning, blockchain, and beyond.</p>
</div>

<div class="ecosystem-item">
  <p><strong>BRC (Big Research Cloud)</strong> – Our robust data platform, offering access to diverse and rich datasets for hands-on exploration.</p>
</div>

<div class="ecosystem-item">
  <p><strong>IDA (Institute for Digital Assets)</strong> – The research institute managing and guiding the entire ecosystem with vision, rigor, and innovation.</p>
</div>

<p>We built this ecosystem to foster collaboration, learning, and cutting-edge research in quantitative science. Whether you're a student, a researcher, or a professional, there's something here for you.</p>

<div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
  <h3><strong>Explore the ecosystem</strong>:</h3>
  <a href="https://quantinar.com"><img width="50px" src="${url.resourcesUrl}/img/quantinar.png" alt="Quantinar Logo"></a>
  <a href="https://quantlet.com"><img width="50px" src="${url.resourcesUrl}/img/quantlet.png" alt="Quantlet Logo"></a>
  <a href="https://theida.net"> <img width="50px" src="${url.resourcesUrl}/img/ida.png" alt="IDA Logo"></a>
  <a href="https://blockchain-research-center.com"><img width="50px" src="${url.resourcesUrl}/img/brc.png" alt="BRC Logo"></a>
</div>

<p><strong>Stay in the loop</strong> – follow us on LinkedIn for updates, job opportunities, new content, and event announcements: <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/ida-ro/" class="icon-text text-ida-linkedin">IDA on LinkedIn <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-linkedin" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
